NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
E.B., Defendant,
and
N.B., Defendant-Petitioner. In the Matter of the Guardianship of N.P.B. and A.B., Minors-Respondents. C-905 September Term 2017
080555 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-2856/2857-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
